HTML is used to create HTML elements
CSS used to style those elements
Javascript is used to create,update and change the style of those HTML elements in your webpage dynamically( launched by netscape in 1995).
Javascript code will be written inside the script tag.This tag will be written inside the html code.
<script type="text/Javascript">
</script>
 -type attribute specifies the type of script the we are gonna use inside the script tag.

:simple html code which includes javascript-
 <!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title></title>
      <script type="text/javascript">
        alert("Hello Javascript")
</script>
</head>
<body>

</body>
</html>

alert function alerts a value in the browser ,its like a print statement of most programming languages but instead of printing a value it will show the msg in the alert box.
